      • visit

        public void visit(int classFileVersionNumber,
                  int modifier,
                  String internalName,
                  String signature,
                  String superTypeName,
                  String[] interfaceName)
        从类复制的说明: ClassVisitor
        Visits the header of the class.
        覆盖:
        visit 在类中 ClassVisitor
        参数:
        classFileVersionNumber - the class version.
        modifier - the class's access flags (see Opcodes). This parameter also indicates if the class is deprecated.
        internalName - the internal name of the class (see getInternalName).
        signature - the signature of this class. May be null if the class is not a generic one, and does not extend or implement generic classes or interfaces.
        superTypeName - the internal of name of the super class (see getInternalName). For interfaces, the super class is Object. May be null, but only for the Object class.
        interfaceName - the internal names of the class's interfaces (see getInternalName). May be null.
